svg.title: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altocumulus translucidus or opacus in two or more layers, or altocumulus opacus in a single layer, not progressively invading the sky, or altocumulus with altostratus or nimbostratus
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altocumulus in two or more layers, usually opaque in places, and not progressively invading the sky; or opaque layer of altocumulus, not progressively invading the sky; or altocumulus together with altostratus or nimbostratus
